{"tid":1723384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業 [ 咳嗽師 ] 配合文宣 催淚彈 山埃 二噁英","createTime":"2019-11-15T07:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:30:05.000Z","uid":264071,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bc6eee92f67c06050e1eab1d769e7ed7911a4af5","tid":1723384,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"行動配合文宣 催淚彈毒害 咳嗽加戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家覺得街上多左人咳，可能係轉季咳，但更大可能係<span style=\"color: red;\">催淚彈嘅中毒咳</span>，無論邊樣引發都好，廢老港豬都會一齊咳。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">行動</span><br />\n無論大家真咳假咳都好，都<span style=\"color: red;\">帶翻個口罩，為已為人，注意個人衛生</span>。<br />\n又可以係啲藍絲隔離咳，或者見人地咳，就同隔離朋友仔講「差佬成日亂鳩咁射，路又射屋又射，啲催淚彈好撚毒咖嘛，又有山埃又有二噁英，咳死人」(自由發揮)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣</span><br />\n要大大力宣傳，話比全世界知，香港警察四處放毒，香港政府毒殺人民。<br />\n催淚彈山埃二噁英引發咩後遺症，好多文宣有講，但有樣野寫漏左嘅係 <span style=\"color: red;\">咳嗽</span>，希望之後嘅文宣都加翻落去。<br />\n<br />\n大家記得咳就戴翻口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qE97CC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqE97CC2.jpg&h=5fd74138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LCPGG4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLCPGG4J.jpg&h=4a5b2a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/647kXC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F647kXC4.jpg&h=9e75566d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bm8DKh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBm8DKh5.jpg&h=84ce95c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAJ4ERs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAJ4ERs.png&h=856a945d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"307d1ca3216be2519aa209d508f93c9d8b07abb0","tid":1723384,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl